{"tid":1016213,"cid":31,"subCid":0,"title":"其實香港人點解要就哂班大陸西？？？","createTime":"2019-02-10T16:12:49.000Z","updateTime":"2019-02-11T12:47:12.000Z","uid":2249,"like":197,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":24,"replies":[{"pid":"3280770da12e534ce80c6bc686d774b3fe22f19e","tid":1016213,"uid":2249,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-02-10T16:12:49.000Z","msg":"我係喺旅遊區返工既，每日返工都要對住好多大陸客<br />\n好多時我同佢地講廣東話，佢地就會話：<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">我聽不懂，你講普通話！<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/devil.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> </span></span><br />\n我繼續用廣東話同佢講野，結果佢又聽得明咖喎<br />\n所以班仆街大陸西根本就係識聽，只係想人就佢<br />\n<br />\n我係公司入面少數堅持用廣東話既人，身邊好多同事見到啲大陸西就自動轉channel<br />\n我唔明香港既服務業點解咁撚古怪<br />\n呢度香港嚟咖嘛，香港人講廣東話咖嘛<br />\n有乜理由要我地香港人去講支那話？<br />\n班大陸西去到外國係咪又要人同佢講普通話？<br />\n（我去日本真係見過條蝗婦對住個日本妹狂講支那話，個日本妹R撚爆頭）<br />\n<br />\n我希望睇到呢度而又係做服務業既你<br />\n對住啲大陸西唔好讓步，請你要堅持用廣東話<br />\n我好怕終有一日買野比錢無人會再講廣東話<br />\n我地要比班大陸西知道，呢度係香港，係講廣東話既<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fuck.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7f9dac0818096beb802c44eb601d1d5d007d5918","tid":1016213,"uid":29606,"like":2,"dislike":97,"score":-95,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-02-10T16:22:46.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"62853fe4e5ba21b225b87c498dcfd3cbbfedb087","tid":1016213,"uid":8271,"like":66,"dislike":1,"score":65,"quote":{"pid":"7f9dac0818096beb802c44eb601d1d5d007d5918","tid":1016213,"uid":29606,"like":2,"dislike":97,"score":-95,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-02-10T16:22:46.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-02-10T16:35:10.000Z","msg":"你知唔知乜撚野係中文呀屌你老母死傻閪<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n你自己打撚緊嗰幾隻字又係乜撚野文黎架屌你老母死傻閪<img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/clown4.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a69d1453347b35220d89b414a39a0b1b189aacf2","tid":1016213,"uid":29606,"like":2,"dislike":68,"score":-66,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-02-10T16:36:48.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"683f03889244046c81009f738d331de24d833447","tid":1016213,"uid":125168,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-10T16:43:24.000Z","msg":"其實由得佢地手指指咁溝通咪得<br />\n去旅行自己做遊客個時都係少少當地語言+手勢+英文搞掂架啦"},{"pid":"f652ff1df882d6bfa0325d8fafc11b5ff80d5ecd","tid":1016213,"uid":214344,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-02-10T16:43:27.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"587b1ee9f5ec9421fff19cbc653f7b759ee69928","tid":1016213,"uid":8271,"like":22,"dislike":0,"score":22,"quote":{"pid":"a69d1453347b35220d89b414a39a0b1b189aacf2","tid":1016213,"uid":29606,"like":2,"dislike":68,"score":-66,"quote":{"pid":"62853fe4e5ba21b225b87c498dcfd3cbbfedb087","tid":1016213,"uid":8271,"like":66,"dislike":1,"score":65,"quote":{"pid":"7f9dac0818096beb802c44eb601d1d5d007d5918","tid":1016213,"uid":29606,"like":2,"dislike":97,"score":-95,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-02-10T16:22:46.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-02-10T16:35:10.000Z","msg":"你知唔知乜撚野係中文呀屌你老母死傻閪<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n你自己打撚緊嗰幾隻字又係乜撚野文黎架屌你老母死傻閪<img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/clown4.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-02-10T16:36:48.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-02-10T16:43:48.000Z","msg":"關閪事，旅遊業一向都唔係靠語言黎維持<img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/clown4.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n日本韓國大把地方舖頭嘅人英文水平同香港小學程度差唔多，廣東話更加係0，蝗語都係因為近年班蝗煩到人地要去就佢地，所以先開始引入啲蝗語職員，你覺得其他地方嘅旅遊業咁興盛係因為佢地會講其他語言<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"683c79177f7ee07c6b86ae9b70a5fc2f8143e46a","tid":1016213,"uid":29606,"like":2,"dislike":21,"score":-19,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-02-10T16:47:07.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"323e542960477279a8f204fce0b4091f730cc15d","tid":1016213,"uid":29606,"like":0,"dislike":13,"score":-13,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-02-10T16:49:51.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"e1c13d93fb9c3f190faaeecf3283bb00c0f4bf89","tid":1016213,"uid":8271,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"quote":{"pid":"683c79177f7ee07c6b86ae9b70a5fc2f8143e46a","tid":1016213,"uid":29606,"like":2,"dislike":21,"score":-19,"quote":{"pid":"f652ff1df882d6bfa0325d8fafc11b5ff80d5ecd","tid":1016213,"uid":214344,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"quote":{"pid":"a69d1453347b35220d89b414a39a0b1b189aacf2","tid":1016213,"uid":29606,"like":2,"dislike":68,"score":-66,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-02-10T16:36:48.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-02-10T16:43:27.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-02-10T16:47:07.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-02-10T16:52:40.000Z","msg":"差唔多全世界嘅人去到外國都係用英文溝通架啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/clown4.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n就算係韓國人、日本人、西班牙人、法國人、德國人，仲有好多好多唔同國藉嘅人黎到香港，同我地講佢地嘅語言，我地都係同番佢地講英文架啦，我又無見過有其他國家嘅人黎到香港叫我地同佢講番佢嘅語言喎<img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/clown4.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n再唔係你去睇下機場個TOWER用緊乜野語言黎同全世界嘅機師溝通，大陸機師黎到香港又會用乜野語言同TOWER對話<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2d2a808b2519246faba2c7f05f2d055491534497","tid":1016213,"uid":8271,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"quote":{"pid":"323e542960477279a8f204fce0b4091f730cc15d","tid":1016213,"uid":29606,"like":0,"dislike":13,"score":-13,"quote":{"pid":"587b1ee9f5ec9421fff19cbc653f7b759ee69928","tid":1016213,"uid":8271,"like":22,"dislike":0,"score":22,"quote":{"pid":"a69d1453347b35220d89b414a39a0b1b189aacf2","tid":1016213,"uid":29606,"like":2,"dislike":68,"score":-66,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-02-10T16:36:48.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-02-10T16:43:48.000Z","msg":"關閪事，旅遊業一向都唔係靠語言黎維持<img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/clown4.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n日本韓國大把地方舖頭嘅人英文水平同香港小學程度差唔多，廣東話更加係0，蝗語都係因為近年班蝗煩到人地要去就佢地，所以先開始引入啲蝗語職員，你覺得其他地方嘅旅遊業咁興盛係因為佢地會講其他語言<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-02-10T16:49:51.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-02-10T16:53:53.000Z","msg":"依家唔係講緊職員本身識唔識講，係講緊班客迫你講，你理解下人地講乜先啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/clown4.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e773f2dd0d2fce626d3172709c09ffcd370bb60b","tid":1016213,"uid":2249,"like":17,"dislike":0,"score":17,"quote":{"pid":"683c79177f7ee07c6b86ae9b70a5fc2f8143e46a","tid":1016213,"uid":29606,"like":2,"dislike":21,"score":-19,"quote":{"pid":"f652ff1df882d6bfa0325d8fafc11b5ff80d5ecd","tid":1016213,"uid":214344,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"quote":{"pid":"a69d1453347b35220d89b414a39a0b1b189aacf2","tid":1016213,"uid":29606,"like":2,"dislike":68,"score":-66,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-02-10T16:36:48.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-02-10T16:43:27.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-02-10T16:47:07.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-10T16:53:59.000Z","msg":"英文係國際語言嘛<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n你去第度旅行唔識都係講英文先啦<br />\n我serve過啲日本人韓國人，行到埋嚟都係講英文，唔會assume我識聽日文韓文啦<br />\n<br />\n所以我依家係講緊啲大陸西既態度<br />\n佢地當正全世界都係講支那話<br />\n用一副至高無上既態度要全世界就佢地<br />\n我睇唔過眼既係點解香港人要自甘墮落，自己除埋褲任由啲大陸西每日強姦我地呀<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fuck.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"db31fd6706ec1d38c2c47d71758451ada2f5da9a","tid":1016213,"uid":38456,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-10T16:55:06.000Z","msg":"這就是傻仔香港人 包括老闆或樓上扮老闆(如有)"},{"pid":"1a88fac69ea9eeea8f7a64d7782e8a7c0c39675c","tid":1016213,"uid":29606,"like":0,"dislike":9,"score":-9,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-02-10T17:01:51.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"0f2e48a40c1b82b0cadc2897095799c6e09a31ba","tid":1016213,"uid":76848,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"2d2a808b2519246faba2c7f05f2d055491534497","tid":1016213,"uid":8271,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"quote":{"pid":"323e542960477279a8f204fce0b4091f730cc15d","tid":1016213,"uid":29606,"like":0,"dislike":13,"score":-13,"quote":{"pid":"587b1ee9f5ec9421fff19cbc653f7b759ee69928","tid":1016213,"uid":8271,"like":22,"dislike":0,"score":22,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-02-10T16:43:48.000Z","msg":"關閪事，旅遊業一向都唔係靠語言黎維持<img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/clown4.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n日本韓國大把地方舖頭嘅人英文水平同香港小學程度差唔多，廣東話更加係0，蝗語都係因為近年班蝗煩到人地要去就佢地，所以先開始引入啲蝗語職員，你覺得其他地方嘅旅遊業咁興盛係因為佢地會講其他語言<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-02-10T16:49:51.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-02-10T16:53:53.000Z","msg":"依家唔係講緊職員本身識唔識講，係講緊班客迫你講，你理解下人地講乜先啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/clown4.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-10T17:03:07.000Z","msg":"人哋請人阿 洗閪理解人講乜咩<img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"82cc589966af9f4f9fddbc8130739af2d6f8709c","tid":1016213,"uid":8271,"like":3,"dislike":1,"score":2,"quote":{"pid":"1a88fac69ea9eeea8f7a64d7782e8a7c0c39675c","tid":1016213,"uid":29606,"like":0,"dislike":9,"score":-9,"quote":{"pid":"e1c13d93fb9c3f190faaeecf3283bb00c0f4bf89","tid":1016213,"uid":8271,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"quote":{"pid":"683c79177f7ee07c6b86ae9b70a5fc2f8143e46a","tid":1016213,"uid":29606,"like":2,"dislike":21,"score":-19,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-02-10T16:47:07.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-02-10T16:52:40.000Z","msg":"差唔多全世界嘅人去到外國都係用英文溝通架啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/clown4.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n就算係韓國人、日本人、西班牙人、法國人、德國人，仲有好多好多唔同國藉嘅人黎到香港，同我地講佢地嘅語言，我地都係同番佢地講英文架啦，我又無見過有其他國家嘅人黎到香港叫我地同佢講番佢嘅語言喎<img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/clown4.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n再唔係你去睇下機場個TOWER用緊乜野語言黎同全世界嘅機師溝通，大陸機師黎到香港又會用乜野語言同TOWER對話<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-02-10T17:01:51.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-02-10T17:09:12.000Z","msg":"屌奶星，依家唔係講緊職員本身識唔識講，係講緊班客迫你講，你理解下人地講乜先啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/clown4.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"fccf8dd25364380584f905e93a876902c0e0a914","tid":1016213,"uid":4448,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-10T17:12:20.000Z","msg":"同意樓主"},